<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>中国新闻|今日突发新闻|路透社</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/</link><description>Reuters.com 是您获取最新中国新闻故事和时事的在线来源，确保我们的读者及时了解任何突发新闻动态 - RSSHub 用爱制作(https://github.com/DIYgod/RSSHub)</description><lastBuildDate>Tue, 23 Apr 2024 06:15:37 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>中国将修订统计法打击数据造假</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/china-revise-statistics-law-fight-data-fraud-2024-04-23/</link><description>官方媒体新华社周二表示，由于人们对世界第二大经济体数据的可靠性表示怀疑，中国将修改统计法，以打击持续存在的数据欺诈行为。</description><pubDate>Tue, 23 Apr 2024 05:19:59 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china/china-revise-statistics-law-fight-data-fraud-2024-04-23/</guid></item><item><title>联合国气象机构称亚洲是受气候灾害影响最严重的地区</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/asia-is-most-climate-disaster-impacted-region-un-meteorological-agency-says-2024-04-23/</link><description>世界气象组织（WMO）表示，去年亚洲是世界上受气候相关灾害影响最严重的地区，其中洪水和风暴造成的伤亡人数最多。</description><pubDate>Tue, 23 Apr 2024 05:04:01 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/asia-is-most-climate-disaster-impacted-region-un-meteorological-agency-says-2024-04-23/</guid></item><item><title>IEA表示，电动汽车销量将上升，但可负担性成为焦点</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/electric-car-sales-rise-affordability-focus-iea-says-2024-04-23/</link><description>国际能源署 (IEA) 周二预测，尽管一些市场面临经济阻力，但电动汽车销量将在 2024 年强劲增长，但负担能力和充电基础设施将是未来增长的关键。</description><pubDate>Tue, 23 Apr 2024 05:03:47 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/electric-car-sales-rise-affordability-focus-iea-says-2024-04-23/</guid></item><item><title>《华尔街日报》报道，美国将瞄准援助俄罗斯战争的中国银行</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/us-take-aim-chinese-banks-aiding-russia-war-effort-wsj-reports-2024-04-23/</link><description>《华尔街日报》周一援引知情人士的话报道称，美国正在起草制裁措施，威胁要切断一些中国银行与全球金融体系的联系，官员们希望这将阻止北京对俄罗斯军事生产的商业支持。</description><pubDate>Tue, 23 Apr 2024 04:10:23 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/us-take-aim-chinese-banks-aiding-russia-war-effort-wsj-reports-2024-04-23/</guid></item><item><title>独家：招标显示中国最近收购了超微、戴尔服务器中禁用的英伟达芯片</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/china-acquired-recently-banned-nvidia-chips-super-micro-dell-servers-tenders-2024-04-23/</link><description>尽管美国去年扩大了向中国出售此类技术的禁令，但中国的大学和研究机构最近通过经销商获得了高端英伟达人工智能芯片。</description><pubDate>Tue, 23 Apr 2024 03:34:30 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china/china-acquired-recently-banned-nvidia-chips-super-micro-dell-servers-tenders-2024-04-23/</guid></item><item><title>亚洲股市在科技财报公布前扩大涨幅，日元脆弱</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/global-markets-wrapup-1-2024-04-23/</link><description>亚洲股市周二延续涨势，受到华尔街的影响，投资者的注意力转向本周美国科技巨头的盈利报告，而美元依然坚挺，迫使日元跌至 34 年来的新低。</description><pubDate>Tue, 23 Apr 2024 02:18:50 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/global-markets-wrapup-1-2024-04-23/</guid></item><item><title>Tea shop chain Sichuan Baicha Baidao shares slump 38% in Hong Kong debut</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/retail-consumer/tea-shop-chain-sichuan-baicha-baidao-shares-slump-23-hong-kong-debut-2024-04-23/</link><description>中国茶叶连锁店四川白茶百岛实业在完成 3.3 亿美元的首次公开募股 (IPO) 后，周二在香港上市时股价下跌 38.3%。</description><pubDate>Tue, 23 Apr 2024 01:57:57 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/retail-consumer/tea-shop-chain-sichuan-baicha-baidao-shares-slump-23-hong-kong-debut-2024-04-23/</guid></item><item><title>所罗门群岛面临选举结果的紧张等待</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/solomon-islands-faces-tense-wait-election-results-2024-04-22/</link><description>所罗门群岛面临着选举结果的紧张等待，因为反对党领先于现任总理马内塞·索加瓦雷领导的我们党，周二的计票结果显示，独立人士将是组建政府的关键。</description><pubDate>Mon, 22 Apr 2024 23:34:52 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/solomon-islands-faces-tense-wait-election-results-2024-04-22/</guid></item><item><title>美国和韩国本周将就美军费用举行会谈</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/aerospace-defense/us-south-korea-meet-american-troop-costs-this-week-2024-04-22/</link><description>美国国务院周一表示，美国和韩国官员将于本周在夏威夷会面，就分担驻韩美军的费用进行会谈，美国寻求“公平公正的结果”，以加强两国的联盟。</description><pubDate>Mon, 22 Apr 2024 22:04:48 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/aerospace-defense/us-south-korea-meet-american-troop-costs-this-week-2024-04-22/</guid></item><item><title>早盘竞价：科技行业平静，4 月份 PMI 开始滚动</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/global-markets-view-asia-graphic-pix-2024-04-22/</link><description>展望未来一天的亚洲市场。</description><pubDate>Mon, 22 Apr 2024 21:59:15 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/global-markets-view-asia-graphic-pix-2024-04-22/</guid></item><item><title>官方媒体称朝鲜进行首次“核触发”模拟演习</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/north-koreas-kim-guides-nuclear-counterattack-simulation-drills-kcna-says-2024-04-22/</link><description>朝鲜国家通讯社朝中社周二表示，朝鲜在领导人金正恩的指导下进行了首次核反击演习，以模拟其“核触发”管理系统，这是对其敌人的明确警告。</description><pubDate>Mon, 22 Apr 2024 21:37:36 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/north-koreas-kim-guides-nuclear-counterattack-simulation-drills-kcna-says-2024-04-22/</guid></item><item><title>特朗普称拜登将对任何 TikTok 禁令“负责”</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/us/trump-says-biden-would-be-responsible-any-tiktok-ban-2024-04-22/</link><description>共和党总统候选人唐纳德·特朗普周一表示，总统乔·拜登正在“推动”对 TikTok 的禁令，如果实施禁令，他将承担责任，并敦促选民注意。</description><pubDate>Mon, 22 Apr 2024 20:18:49 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/us/trump-says-biden-would-be-responsible-any-tiktok-ban-2024-04-22/</guid></item><item><title>台湾发生6.3级地震，目前尚无受损报告</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/taiwan-rattled-by-63-magnitude-quake-no-immediate-reports-damage-2024-04-22/</link><description>台湾气象部门表示，周二，台湾东部花莲县发生了 6.3 级地震，目前尚未收到受损情况报告。</description><pubDate>Mon, 22 Apr 2024 18:48:20 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/taiwan-rattled-by-63-magnitude-quake-no-immediate-reports-damage-2024-04-22/</guid></item><item><title>布林肯访华前报告称新疆种族灭绝仍在继续</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/blinken-says-genocide-xinjiang-is-ongoing-report-ahead-china-visit-2024-04-22/</link><description>美国国务卿安东尼·布林肯在本周计划访问中国之前发表的一份报告中表示，北京继续在西部新疆省对维吾尔族和其他穆斯林少数民族犯下种族灭绝和反人类罪。</description><pubDate>Mon, 22 Apr 2024 18:02:11 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/blinken-says-genocide-xinjiang-is-ongoing-report-ahead-china-visit-2024-04-22/</guid></item><item><title>独家：随着石油制裁的回归，委内瑞拉将加速加密货币转型</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/finance/venezuela-accelerate-cryptocurrency-shift-oil-sanctions-return-2024-04-22/</link><description>三名知情人士表示，随着美国重新对该国实施石油制裁，委内瑞拉国营石油公司 PDVSA 计划增加其原油和燃料出口中数字货币的使用。</description><pubDate>Mon, 22 Apr 2024 16:19:01 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/finance/venezuela-accelerate-cryptocurrency-shift-oil-sanctions-return-2024-04-22/</guid></item></channel></rss>